data.description: Just listed! Discover your next home with this charming 3 bed, 1 bath gem on a spacious .45 acre lot. Enjoy the large back yard and screened-in front porch. This 1410 sq ft residence has an eat-in kitchen, spacious living room and a versatile building attached for storage or potential living space. Updates include a new roof (November 2022) and new windows and siding on the front side of the house. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
